OL,3,CBacklash over council weed removal plan
OL,5,FMore than 7,500 people have signed a
OL,6,Fpetition against Cornwall Council's
OL,7,Fplans to use chemicals to tackle weeds
OL,8,Fon pavements.
OL,10,FCornwall Council stopped using
OL,11,Fchemicals to remove weeds from
OL,12,Fhighways 13 years ago but says the
OL,13,Ftargeted application of glyphosate
OL,14,Fwould begin next month.
OL,16,F200 health professionals in Cornwall
OL,17,Fhave also signed a letter warning
OL,18,Fabout the dangers of the chemical
OL,19,Fglyphosate.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
