OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1776618353
OL,3,CBacklash over council weed removal plan
OL,5,FThe letter, led by Hayle GP Dr Robert
OL,6,FCook, urges Cornwall Council think
OL,7,Fagain with the backdrop of "growing
OL,8,Fscientific evidence" highlighting the
OL,9,Fhealth risks associated with
OL,10,Fglyphosate.
OL,12,FThe undersigned point to the World
OL,13,FHealth Organization (WHO) research
OL,14,Fwhich classified the chemical as
OL,15,F"probably carcinogenic to humans" in
OL,16,F2015.
OL,18,FCornish town and parish councils join
OL,19,Fthose who have expressed concerns
OL,20,Fabout the dangers to the environment.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
