OL,3,CBacklash over council weed removal plan
OL,5,FThe local authority dismissed these
OL,6,Fconcerns saying it was the most
OL,7,Feffective way to tackle weeds.
OL,9,FCllr Dan Rogerson, the Cabinet member
OL,10,Ffor Transport, says they have piloted
OL,11,Fother methods including mechanical
OL,12,Fremoval, burning and the use of
OL,13,Fvinegar but these are "time consuming"
OL,14,Fand "none of those things have really
OL,15,Fworked".
OL,17,FThe council says by using a targeted
OL,18,Fdrop method and diluting the chemical
OL,19,F1 to 40 parts with water that will
OL,20,Fminimise any negative effects.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
