CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1776618353
OL,3,CBacklash over council weed removal plan
OL,5,FCllr Rogerson says they have received
OL,6,Fmore than 2,000 complaints over the
OL,7,Fpast three years about weeds and
OL,8,F"people feel that they they look
OL,9,Fneglected" if they are not dealt with.
OL,11,FPenzance Town Council is one of
OL,12,Fseveral who have expressed their
OL,13,Fdisappointment at this decision saying
OL,14,Fthey local authority has not given
OL,15,Fthem enough notice to look at
OL,16,Falternatives.
OL,18,FThe town uses mechanical methods to
OL,19,Fremove weeds from the public spaces
OL,20,Fthey are responsible for such as
OL,21,FPenlee Park.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
