PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1776618353
OL,3,CBacklash over council weed removal plan
OL,5,FMayor of Penzance, Stephen Reynolds,
OL,6,Ftold ITV West Country "We live right
OL,7,Fon the edge of a fragile ecosystem
OL,8,Fwith the sea and (non chemical
OL,9,Fmethods) have proved really popular.
OL,10,FAnd that has been shown by the number
OL,11,Fof people who've come to us, since
OL,12,FCornwall Council announced that
OL,13,Fdecision, and said, do not let
OL,14,FCornwall Council start spraying again."
OL,16,FCornwall Council are expected to
OL,17,Fdebate a proposal for public
OL,18,Fconsultation on the weed treatment
OL,19,Fprogramme on Tuesday 21 April.
OL,26,@pD@RpmqD@Hpn
